<div class="nd-companion__shell">

  <section class="nd-campaign-context" aria-label="Campaign Context">
    <div class="nd-campaign-context__item" data-context="scene" hidden>
      <span class="nd-campaign-context__label">Scene</span>
      <span class="nd-campaign-context__value" data-context-value></span>
    </div>
    <div class="nd-campaign-context__item" data-context="focus">
      <span class="nd-campaign-context__label">Focus</span>
      <span class="nd-campaign-context__value" data-context-value>Party</span>
    </div>
    <div class="nd-campaign-context__item" data-context="combat" hidden>
      <span class="nd-campaign-context__label">Combat</span>
      <span class="nd-campaign-context__value" data-context-value></span>
    </div>
    <div class="nd-campaign-context__item" data-context="round" hidden>
      <span class="nd-campaign-context__label">Round</span>
      <span class="nd-campaign-context__value" data-context-value></span>
    </div>
    <div class="nd-campaign-context__item" data-context="turn" hidden>
      <span class="nd-campaign-context__label">Turn</span>
      <span class="nd-campaign-context__value" data-context-value></span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="nd-focus-panel" data-focus-panel data-focus-kind="party" aria-label="Focus">
    <img class="nd-focus-panel__portrait" data-focus="portrait" alt="" hidden>
    <div class="nd-focus-panel__meta">
      <div class="nd-focus-panel__name" data-focus="name">Party</div>
      <div class="nd-focus-panel__type" data-focus-row="type" hidden>
        <span class="nd-focus-panel__type-label">Type</span>
        <span class="nd-focus-panel__type-value" data-focus="type"></span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="nd-companion__row">

    <article class="nd-card nd-card--beat">
      <header class="nd-card__header">
        <span class="nd-card__accent" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <h2 class="nd-card__label">Current Beat</h2>
        <span class="nd-live-notes__status" data-live-notes-status hidden></span>
      </header>
      <div
        class="nd-card__text nd-live-notes"
        data-storage="currentBeat"
        data-placeholder="Click here to start typing..."
        role="textbox"
        aria-label="Current Beat"
      ></div>
    </article>

    <article class="nd-card nd-card--scene">
      <header class="nd-card__header">
        <span class="nd-card__accent" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <h2 class="nd-card__label">Next Scene</h2>
      </header>
      <p class="nd-card__text">
        Edric's enforcers breach the archive front door — the party must choose: fight their way
        out, negotiate, or use the secret passage Maren hinted at (DC 14 Investigation to find it
        in time).
      </p>
      <ul class="nd-tag-list">
        <li class="nd-tag nd-tag--scene">Encounter</li>
        <li class="nd-tag nd-tag--danger">Combat possible</li>
      </ul>
    </article>

  </section>

  <article class="nd-card nd-card--threads">
    <header class="nd-card__header">
      <span class="nd-card__accent" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <h2 class="nd-card__label">Open Threads</h2>
    </header>
    <ul class="nd-thread-list">
      <li class="nd-thread-list__item">
        <span class="nd-thread-list__marker" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="nd-thread-list__text">Investigate who burned the Millhaven granary</span>
      </li>
      <li class="nd-thread-list__item">
        <span class="nd-thread-list__marker" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="nd-thread-list__text">Track down the Pale Merchant's ledger</span>
      </li>
      <li class="nd-thread-list__item nd-thread-list__item--done">
        <span class="nd-thread-list__marker" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="nd-thread-list__text">Return the stolen sextant to Captain Voss</span>
      </li>
      <li class="nd-thread-list__item">
        <span class="nd-thread-list__marker" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="nd-thread-list__text">Discover why the Thornwood has gone silent</span>
      </li>
      <li class="nd-thread-list__item">
        <span class="nd-thread-list__marker" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="nd-thread-list__text">Deliver the letter to Sister Elara in Ashfeld</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </article>

  <footer class="nd-companion__footer">
    <button type="button" class="nd-oh-shit-button">
      <span class="nd-oh-shit-button__icon" aria-hidden="true">⚠</span>
      OH SHIT!
    </button>
  </footer>

</div>
